		<div>I personally dislike the sale of game items or characters for cash.  <br />
<br />
It is bad enough to compete with people farming items to sell for plat, but generally those people don't make a full time business of it, since their goal is usually just better equipment for the character they are playing.<br />
<br />
Individuals farming gear for RL profit go a step beyond that, they're competing with you in game to pay their rent.  Most of these people aren't playing the game, their farming items to sell to you, items that you could probably have gotten on your own if they weren't farming them.<br />
<br />
Companies who make a business out of farming and selling EQ items takes it the extreme.  Now you potentially have groups of dedicated farmers who could totally dominate specific loot drops, pretty much requiring you to buy an item from them.<br />
<br />
The only person these people are helping is themselves, at the expense of everyone else who plays the game.</div>
