				Dear Sir<br />
<br />
We would like to clear up a few issues with your news post. Forrest Parker, one member of black snow last worked for Obsidian Technologies 1/2001. A previous member, Wes, was let go 10/2001. We have in the past allowed ex employees to keep their email as a courtesy, but all emails have now been suspended. We are in no way, shape or form connected to black snow, and have received no compensation of any kind from them or any member of their group, either personally or through Obsidian Technologies. We have already spoken to the people at Mythic, and will be happy to speak with any other interested parties involved in this debacle. Obsidian Technologies and it's partners have absolutely nothing to do with this group. Please feel free to contact me if you need further information. <br />
